{"tid":1778348,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（清算開始）教育局稱30宗涉老師操守調查初步成立　正考慮懲處","createTime":"2019-12-11T01:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T11:08:02.000Z","uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e63b143be20e5a1f526f38aa37a4ef20ba96fe85","tid":1778348,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T01:17:02.000Z","msg":"藍絲就唔洗罰 好似係<br />\n<br />\n一名教師昨日被捕，教育局表示，已要求學校履行作為僱主以及確保學生安全的責任，考慮暫停該教師的職務。<br />\n<br />\n教育局表示，十分重視教師的專業操守及學生的行為，指教師的言行須符合社會的道德及專業方面的期望，局方會嚴肅跟進每個被判罪、被捕及被投訴的老師個案。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，自6月中至上月初，教育局已就106宗與近期社會事件有關的教師專業操守個案展開調查，目前已初步完成60宗個案，包括早前已發出譴責信的兩宗個案，當中約30宗初步成立，教育局正考慮應作出的懲處。<br />\n<br />\n至於被捕教師的數目，發言人說，由於涉及法律程序，局方現階段不便置評，但教育局會根據《教育條例》嚴肅跟進違法的教師，如果情況嚴重，可以取消註冊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497021-20191210.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR3XC96TDUIOd_u4yOIQAfQVXbWmbldaQLRSdbCM20zjO2yUFdt17K1gZJU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497021-20191210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR3XC96TDUIOd_u4yOIQAfQVXbWmbldaQLRSdbCM20zjO2yUFdt17K1gZJU&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwu9tl09raJ%2B2zMWOssuGUT0%3D&h=9155169d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497021-20191210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR3XC96TDUIOd_u4yOIQAfQVXbWmbldaQLRSdbCM20zjO2yUFdt17K1gZJU&h=a4eb8ed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497021-20191210.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR3XC96TDUIOd_u4yOIQAfQVXbWmbldaQLRSdbCM20zjO2yUFdt17K1gZJU</a>"},{"pid":"2cfc3c6e02279c0162b8724caef31c0bbd2f9abb","tid":1778348,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T01:17:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">適逢依家係國際人權日<br />\n快啲去Twitter同全世界講下香港被打壓的情況！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.g